# encoding: utf-8

<style type="text/css" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html">
    #gallery {
        height: 450px;
        width: 780px;
    }
</style>


<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<div class="service-left-column">
  <div class="service-gallery">
    <div id="gallery">
      <% @service.service_images.each do |service_image| %>
          <a href="<%= service_image.image.url %>">
            <img
            src="<%= service_image.image.url %>" ,
            data-big="<%= service_image.image.url %>">
            <!--data-title="Image title"-->
            <!--data-description="Image description"-->
          </a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="service-description">
    <h2><%= @service.name %></h2>

    <% @service.rate_times = 10 if @service.rate_times.nil? %>

    <div class="left-column">
      <div class="stars">
        <form action="">
          <input class="star star-5" id="star-5" type="radio" disabled name="star" <%= 'checked' unless @service.rate_times.floor > 5 %>/>
          <label class="star star-5" for="star-5"></label>
          <input class="star star-4" id="star-4" type="radio" disabled name="star" <%= 'checked' unless @service.rate_times.floor > 4 %>/>
          <label class="star star-4" for="star-4"></label>
          <input class="star star-3" id="star-3" type="radio" disabled name="star" <%= 'checked' unless @service.rate_times.floor > 3 %>/>
          <label class="star star-3" for="star-3"></label>
          <input class="star star-2" id="star-2" type="radio" disabled name="star" <%= 'checked' unless @service.rate_times.floor > 2 %>/>
          <label class="star star-2" for="star-2"></label>
          <input class="star star-1" id="star-1" type="radio" disabled name="star" <%= 'checked' unless @service.rate_times.floor > 1 %>/>
          <label class="star star-1" for="star-1"></label>

          <div class="clear"></div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <p><%= "#{t('capacity')}: #{@service.capacity}" %></p>

      <p><%= "#{t('location')}: #{@service.location}" %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="right-column">
      <p> <%=  number_to_currency @service.price, unit: 'Tsh ' %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="more-details">
      <div class='tabs'>
        <ul class='horizontal'>
          <li><a href="#tab-1"><%= t('description') %></a></li>
          <li><a href="#tab-2"><%= t('reviews') %></a></li>
          <li><a href="#tab-3">Location map</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div id='tab-1'>
          <%= @service.description.to_s.html_safe %>
        </div>
        <div id='tab-2'>
          It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking
          at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as
          opposed to using 'Content here, content here', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing
          packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for 'lorem ipsum'
          will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by
          accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).
        </div>
        <div id='tab-3'>
          Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's
          standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to
          make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic
          typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset
          sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus
          PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</div>
<div class="service-right-column">
  <% vendor = @service.vendor %>
  <p class="service-titles">Vendor details</p>
<div class="vendor-logo"><%= image_tag vendor.logo.url %></div>
<div class="vendor-details">
<h2><%= @service.vendor.name %></h2>
  <p><%= "#{t('location')}: #{vendor.address}" %></p>
  <p><%= "#{t('phone')}: #{vendor.phone}" %></p>
  <p><%= "#{t('website')}:" %></p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div>

<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $('.tabs').tabslet();
    });

    Galleria.run('#gallery', {
        wait: true,
        debug: true
    });

</script>




